# Rust — format after every edit

After **any** create/edit of a `.rs` file in this repo:

1. Run `cargo fmt --all` from the workspace root (`portaki-modules/`).
2. If only one crate was touched and workspace fmt is unavailable, run `cargo fmt` in that crate.
3. Before commit / push: `cargo fmt --all -- --check` must pass (CI `quality` / Format job fails otherwise).

Do not leave unformatted Rust in the working tree. Format in the same turn as the edit — not later.